00:07:01.720 --> 00:07:02.560
Quoi?

00:07:04.760 --> 00:07:05.840
Ne plus jamais concevoir ?

00:07:06.280 --> 00:07:07.400
Précisément.

00:07:07.400 --> 00:07:08.416
Sinon,

00:07:08.800 --> 00:07:10.920
